Package commandbased

Class StartCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • commandbased.Command
      • commandbased.InstantCommand
        • commandbased.StartCommand
  • public class StartCommand
extends InstantCommand
    A StartCommand will call the start() method of another command when it is initialized and will finish immediately.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors

      StartCommand​(Command commandToStart)
      Instantiates a StartCommand which will start the given command whenever its initialize() is called.
